The [[next]] flag is presentation across every question type, so toggling it
must never change the digest.  Without this guarantee, a lecturer flipping a
single slide from \enquote{Next $\rightarrow$} to \enquote{last slide} would
orphan every answer already collected for that question --- the URL prefix
would shift to a fresh hash, and the old QR codes would resolve to nothing.

